sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>9000/TCP
    participant VLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP

    Note over S3,HF: Flow 2 - Model Loading (Startup)
    S3->>HF: Model weights download<br/>HTTP/9000, AWS IAM credentials
    Note over HF: Load model into memory<br/>(SeqClass/TokClass/GraniteLM)

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Orchestrator,BuiltIn: Flow 1 - Built-in Content Detection
        Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP, Istio mTLS
        Istio->>BuiltIn: Forward request<br/>mTLS terminated
        Note over BuiltIn: Local processing:<br/>Regex PII scan<br/>File format validation<br/>Custom Python detectors
        BuiltIn-->>Istio: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>(detections with spans + scores)
        Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>Istio mTLS
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over Orchestrator,HF: Flow 2 - HuggingFace Model Classification
        Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP, Istio mTLS
        Istio->>HF: Forward request<br/>mTLS terminated
        Note over HF: Tokenize input<br/>Model forward pass<br/>Softmax → labels + scores
        HF-->>Istio: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>(classifications with confidence)
        Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>Istio mTLS
    end

    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
        Note over Orchestrator,VLLM: Flow 3 - LLM Judge Evaluation
        Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP, Istio mTLS
        Istio->>Judge: Forward request<br/>mTLS terminated
        Judge->>VLLM: OpenAI-compatible chat completion<br/>HTTP/8080, Istio mTLS
        VLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response<br/>(verdict + score)
        Judge-->>Istio: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>(detection with metric score)
        Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>Istio mTLS
    end
